{"tid":1825952,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"『警世』想請槍嘅朋友 入一入嚟","createTime":"2020-01-15T17:42:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-18T17:47:39.000Z","uid":144964,"like":21,"dislike":73,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"2674cfa7c4c76f17d58c5f05510bfc397bddbd84","tid":1825952,"uid":144964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T17:42:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BPpz4v1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBPpz4v1.png&h=127ff896&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n代友post<br />\n<br />\n之前自己做唔切功課 就諗住請槍。呢個page話明 有B以上,亦唔會抄襲， 做唔到會退錢。咁就諗住信佢啦，俾左三份佢做 成7000蚊。<br />\n<br />\n到左我要求 佢俾貨嘅日期，佢遲交俾我。都算！屌你老味 <br />\n佢交埋啲垃圾俾我 一篇大學功課，的確過到電腦 但全部係網上抄返嚟 點解過到電腦啊？<br />\n<br />\n成篇功課 無一句通順，啲字句加埋啲糞便嘅詞語，明明都唔關篇功課事，之後我成篇自己改過<br />\n<br />\n到第二 三份，要交個日先同我講佢 做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好波 又係我自己搞掂<br />\n<br />\n出左嚟嘅成績 份野C-左，我聯絡返佢，話我根本淨係用左一份佢提供嘅請槍文章，另外個兩份抄嘅用唔到，想退返錢。佢就瘋狂已讀不回 原本話退2000蚊 依家影都無埋。<br />\n<br />\n又話自己打手 常春藤出嚟點點點，最後遲交 又交埋啲抄嘅垃圾出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：唔係想博同情 只係想各位手足睇路，想請槍真係三思 唔好好似我咁傻。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0bf7ce295db098198278b478e030321a5e4ec62","tid":1825952,"uid":144964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T17:42:23.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2af9bcb51b3b4c795c9b099ecfbff984cfeed4e7","tid":1825952,"uid":144964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T17:42:33.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6d2d8e5c10ce01a7b68c5d5ab585b329f6f5d5bb","tid":1825952,"uid":144964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T17:42:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8885440daf6f06b07cbcecdff4f1a94078508d3","tid":1825952,"uid":144964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15